OL,3,CFood parcels hit record numbers, as
OL,4,Cpeople 'unable to afford essentials.'
OL,6,F187,400 emergency food parcels were
OL,7,Fprovided to food banks across Wales
OL,8,Flast year, according to a charity -
OL,9,Fmore than ever before.
OL,11,Fsaid that an increasing number of
OL,12,Fpeople were the essentials, with more
OL,13,Fthan 47,700 people in Wales using a
OL,14,Ffood bank for the first time, as many
OL,15,Fpeople as the population of Bridgend.
OL,17,FThe data also indicated that 65
OL,18,Fpercent of the support provided to
OL,19,Ffood banks in 2023 was for families
OL,20,Fwith children.
