OL,6,FRachel Biggs, Manager of Cardiff food
OL,7,Fbank, said: "Across Cardiff we've seen
OL,8,Fneed continue to increase as people
OL,9,Fare unable to afford the essentials;
OL,10,Fthis last financial year we have
OL,11,Fprovided more than 20,000 emergency
OL,12,Ffood parcels to people in need.
