OL,3,CFood parcels hit record numbers, as
OL,4,Cpeople 'unable to afford essentials.'
OL,6,F"For two thirds of people who came to
OL,7,FCardiff Food bank, their only income
OL,8,Fwas benefits, and their top reason for
OL,9,Fneeding support was that they couldn't
OL,10,Fafford the essentials. It simply isn't
OL,11,Fright that our benefits system is
OL,12,Ffailing people and locking them in
OL,13,Fpoverty. We're also hearing from
OL,14,Fpeople whose housing situation is
OL,15,Fforcing them to need to use a food
OL,16,Fbank, and in Wales almost 1 in 3
OL,17,Fchildren is living in poverty.
