OL,6,F"Our vision is a future where no one
OL,7,Fgoes hungry because everyone can
OL,8,Fafford the essentials. We are
OL,9,Fincredibly grateful to the public for
OL,10,Ftheir support with food and financial
OL,11,Fdonations, and we hope to also work
OL,12,Ftogether to use our collective voice
OL,13,Fto bring about lasting change that
OL,14,Fensures that everyone can afford the
OL,15,Fessentials."
