OL,3,CFood parcels hit record numbers, as
OL,4,Cpeople 'unable to afford essentials.'
OL,6,FSpeaking about the rising need for
OL,7,Femergency food, Jo Harry, Network Lead
OL,8,Ffor Wales at the Trussell Trust, said:
OL,9,F"Wales is seeing more and more people,
OL,10,Fparticularly families with children,
OL,11,Funable to afford the essentials needed
OL,12,Fto get by. This is forcing more people
OL,13,Fthrough the doors of food banks than
OL,14,Fever before.
