OL,6,F"Without action, we will be faced with
OL,7,Fanother generation of children who are
OL,8,Fgrowing up believing that food banks
OL,9,Fare a normal part of life ` instead of
OL,10,Fan extraordinary measure to mitigate
OL,11,Fthe failings of our social security
OL,12,Fsystem."
OL,14,FA Welsh Government spokesperson said:
OL,15,F"We have provided #22m to support
OL,16,Fcommunity food organisations to tackle
OL,17,Ffood poverty, and help people maximise
OL,18,Ftheir income and build financial
OL,19,Fresilience.
